                    hence our system can’t accept your voucher codes. You may email your voucher to
                    <a href="mailto:customerservice@photobookmart.com">customerservice@photobookmart.com</a>
                    if you voucher remains valid.</strong></li>
                <li><a id="voucher02" name="voucher02"></a><strong>Our photo books are shipped by professional
                    courier service provider, we are unable to combine your orders and ship at once.
                    Your book is packed in an individual box and the courier services will charge based
                    on per box basis.</strong></li>
                <li><a id="voucher03" name="voucher03"></a><strong>Our system can only accept 1 voucher
                    at a time. You need to place multiple orders.</strong></li>
                <li><a id="voucher04" name="voucher04"></a><strong>Kindly email your vouchers (PDF)
                    to customerservice@photobookmart.com</strong></li>
                <li><a id="voucher05" name="voucher05"></a><strong>You may key in your voucher code
                    as security code</strong></li>
                <li><a id="voucher06" name="voucher06"></a><strong>Click on redemption guide below:
                    <a href="http://www.photobookmart.com/steps.pdf">http://www.photobookmart.com/steps.pdf</a></strong></li>
                <li><a id="voucher07" name="voucher07"></a><strong>It is likely that you’ve selected
                    a photo book that carries a higher price than your voucher’s value. You may refer
                    to our website in your respective country for the price list.</strong></li>
            </ol>
        </ol>
