            <li><a href="#software03">What kind of picture formats can i use for my photo book?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software04">How do i upload my photos to the software?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software05">How do I put my photos on the page?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software06">What is the best resolution for photos in my photo book?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software07">How do I know if my photos are of the minimum required resolution?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software08">What if the resolution of my photos is below the minimum requirement?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software09">I can’t upload my photos on to the software. What should I
                do?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software10">Does Photo Book Editor come with image-enhancing features?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#software11">If I delete or alter my photos on photobook editor, will it
